text: Filip Dvořák (born March 9, 1997) is a Czech professional ice hockey player. He is currently playing for HC ZUBR Přerov of the Czech 1.liga. Dvořák made his Czech Extraliga debut playing with HC Kometa Brno during the 2015-16 Czech Extraliga season. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:HC Kometa Brno players Category:HC ZUBR Přerov players Category:Czech ice hockey forwards Category:Sportspeople from Brno
